  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Precise risk estimation of mortality in cardiac surgery patients is often difficult. Main
      objectives of this study is to calculate mortality probability by two different risk score
      system and to inquire effects of informing anesthesiologist and surgical team; of score of
      the patient; on length of hospitalization and intensive care and also on actualized
      mortality.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
